title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: After learning that Mainadevi grants permission for the wedding, Tarakasura becomes enraged. However, He devises a plan to thwart the marriage.

title: Goopy Bagha Phire Elo
subTitle: Granted three wishes by a benign Goblin king Goopy and Bagha receive food clothes magic slippers and the power to hold people spellbound with music.

subTitle: A fierce fighter against injustice strives to help his middle-class family make ends meet. His dedication lands him a job as a police officer, where he tackles large-scale problems with determination.

subTitle: A determined police officer seeks justice from a man who destroyed his father's life several years ago.

title: Swapner Din
subTitle: Paresh goes on a mission to educate and enlighten the people of rural West Bengal. With many hurdles on his way, he struggles with turning his dream into reality.

subTitle: Vishnu confronts Bali and punishes him after learning about his sinister motive. Tarakasura plans revenge on Vishnu.

title: Bhaijaan Elo Re

subTitle: Megh is forced to take over his father's business and leave behind his whimsical life. He, eventually, falls for one of his employees and tries to win her heart.

title: Jiban Niye Khela
subTitle: In the distant village of Dharampur, Dr Subhankar Sanyal fights the bureaucracy and brings justice to the lives of his patients.

title: Premer Kahini
subTitle: Akash falls in love with Barsha but loses contact with her due to unforeseeable circumstances. While attending a marriage ceremony, he is shocked to realise that the bride is none other than Barsha.

title: Surya
subTitle: Ashok, a businessman, provides shelter to Mahim Halden who kills and takes over his property. Soon, Ashok's son, Surya, sets out to avenge his father's death.

title: Minister Phatakesto
subTitle: Fatakeshto, an MLA turned home minister, vows to rescue the government from a massive financial loss while political thugs create several hurdles for him.

title: Premi
subTitle: Sumit, a football player, loses his leg while trying to save Rahul, his best friend. Fate plays a cruel joke when the girl Rahul loves is about to be married off to Sumit.

title: Haraner Nat Jamai
subTitle: Abhinash tries to get the farmers of Shaliganj village to revolt against their oppressive landlords who are exploiting them incessantly.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: While Parvati attempts to convince Lord Shiva to protect the planet, Tarakasura seeks help from Brahma.

title: Gandaakal

title: Nater Guru
subTitle: A terrible heart attack leaves Sulochana in a vulnerable position. To ease her burdens, Sulochana's daughter reaches out to her estranged husband for help.

title: Mon Mane Na
subTitle: On their way to Siliguri, India, Rahul and Ria bump into each other. While Rahul plans to sell a stolen necklace, Ria is excited to meet her boyfriend.

title: Poran Jaye Jolia Re
subTitle: A young man, Rabin, meets three different women at different stages in his life. The relationship he shares with these women, though very different from each other, help him grow as a person.

title: Dui Prithibi
subTitle: Raised by his widowed mother, Tonmoy is a collegian in love with Moina. He loses his memory after a violent altercation and is taken to his father's friend's house where he falls in love with Farah.
